            <p>Many small and growing businesses start managing leads and customers using Excel spreadsheets. While Excel is easy to use initially, it becomes difficult to manage leads, track follow-ups and monitor sales as business grows.</p>
            <p>This is where CRM software like DivineCRM becomes a better solution. A CRM system helps businesses automate customer management, improve follow-ups and increase conversion rates.</p>
